==Text==
To (Trailblazer):

<div align="center">I yearn to clash with you in the heavens above, yet I must still bear the duty that lies beneath,<br />
for even when the flames of war subside, someone must lead the way to peace.

Words cannot express my gratitude for your salvation,<br />
and I'd only raise this cup of crimson pomegranate honey brew,<br />
to toast to our victory in this life, and our journey through the stars.

Your expedition will be surrounded by wolves and lurking vipers.<br />
If you need the flames of Strife, I shall offer you my Kremnos, along with my blood and bones.<br />
They'll accompany your conquest and aid in your endless victories.

When you return triumphant, I shall raise my glass to you once again.<br />
Mydeimos</div>

